---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Deep Roots Drainage — a North Dakota drain tile company built on quality work and honest service.">
  <section class="bg-primary-dark py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Who We Are</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white">About Deep Roots</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Deep Roots Drainage was founded with a simple mission: protect North Dakota homes and properties with drainage solutions that actually work — and stand behind every job we do.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl h-64 flex items-center justify-center text-earth mb-12">
          [Team Photo]
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Why We Started</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We've seen too many homeowners deal with wet basements, cracked foundations, and drainage companies that over-promise and under-deliver. We started Deep Roots to do things right — quality materials, proper installation, and honest pricing.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">What Sets Us Apart</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We understand North Dakota's clay soil, freeze-thaw cycles, and water table challenges.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Honest Quotes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No surprise charges. We tell you what it costs upfront and stick to it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quality Materials</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We use commercial-grade pipe and materials that last, not the cheapest option at the supply house.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Clean Job Sites</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We treat your property with respect. You won't find a mess when we leave.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
